data.description: Welcome to 69 Cumberland Rd. located in Dutchess Park! This Ranch Style Home has 3 Bedrooms on the Main Level and a Spacious Bedroom on the Lower Level. The Kitchen is Setup with the Chef in Mind, Plenty of Counter Space, Cabinets and a Pantry. 2 Full Baths with One on the Main Level and the other on the Lower Level. Hardwood Floors Throughout. Finished Room in Basement Can be used as a Family Room, Office, Man Cave, etc... Plenty of Storage or Parking with your Detached Garage Boasting High Ceilings to Fit Almost any Vehicle. Many Recent Updates include New Roof, Gutters, Furnace, and Water Heater. Central AC is approx. 8 yrs old. Enjoy BBQ's and Family Gatherings in your Private Backyard with Deck. Located in Walking Distance of a Park, Elementary School, and Ball Fields. Great Commuter Location with Proximity to I84 and the Taconic SP. 69 Cumberland is Waiting for you to Call Home!
